{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6971", "repo": "rails", "body": "Hello, I wonder if this still works if the model doesn't have ID (eg HABTM)?\n\nScenario:\n\n`quizzes_quizzes_lists` **doesn't have ID column** \n\n```sql\nselect * from quizzes_quizzes_lists where quizzes_quizzes_lists.id is NULL;\n```\n\nWill return:\n\n> ERROR 1054 (42S22): Unknown column 'quizzes_quizzes_lists.id' in 'where clause'\n\nI think a better alternative would be:\n\n```sql\nselect * from quizzes_quizzes_lists where 1 = 2;\n```\n\nWill return:\n\n> Empty set (0.00 sec)\n\nWhat do you think?\n\n\n**# Update**\n\nI did a test with the `Edge` model (it has no ID) and broke.", "_id": {"$oid": "5238016dbd3543c15100c12d"}, "issue_id": 6971, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6965726", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6971#issuecomment-6965726", "updated_at": "2012-07-14T01:20:52Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte", "login": "jonduarte", "gravatar_id": "d2b4592f0aaf66034dd97cf9d6e095c8", "html_url": "https://github.com/jonduarte", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/d2b4592f0aaf66034dd97cf9d6e095c8?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd1afd50755d3be7c1e6c8c44a81fade4.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 607123, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonduarte/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-07-13T15:13:5